'''飓风奥托'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Otto}}）是2010年10月令[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]东北部普降暴雨并持续数天的一场飓风。系统源于10月6日在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]以北徘徊的[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]，于次日转变成[[2010年大西洋飓风季|2010年大西洋飓风季]]的第15个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。风暴加速向东北方向前进，于10月8日达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时140公里的最高强度，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属一级飓风标准。由于周围环境不利，气旋开始减弱，于10月10日在[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]以西转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。奥托是[[2008年大西洋飓风季|2008年]]的[[2008年热带风暴劳拉|热带风暴劳拉]]以来首场由亚热带风暴转变而成的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | archivedate = 2015-05-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150510121046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2015-05-07 | deadurl = no | format = TXT }}</ref>

奥托及其前身天气系统在加勒比地区东北部飘流了数天，给[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]、[[维尔京群岛|维尔京群岛]]和波多黎各带去旷日持久的降水，引发大面积洪灾和多起[[山崩|山体滑坡]]。整场风暴没有导致人员丧生，但一共造成价值2200万美元（2010年[[美元|美元]]）的破坏，其中又以道路、房产和基础设施受损严重。奥托之后回转向东北方向移动，逐渐穿越大西洋开放水域，没有再对其它陆地构成影响。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Otto 2010 track.png}}
9月下旬，[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]以东附近洋面有大规模[[热带扰动|扰动天气区]]同两股[[东风波|东风波]]相互作用<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009301146/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009301146 | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025013720/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009301146/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009301146 | author = Richard Pasch | year = 2010 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。扰动天气区以非常缓慢的速度向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向飘移<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025013804/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010011144/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010011144 | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | year = 2010 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010011144/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010011144 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Michael Brennan | deadurl = no }}</ref>，并因强烈[[风切变|风切变]]的影响而无法得到发展，最西侧的东北波也在风切变干扰下消散<ref name="Otto">{{cite web | year = 2010 | archivedate = 2015-04-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150404092814/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/otto2010.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/otto2010.html | title = Hurricane Otto | author = David Roth | publisher = Weather Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-10-18 }}</ref>。虽然强度很弱，但这片长条形的[[低压槽|低压槽]]（[[低气压|低气压区]]）持续了数天，在[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]最东面基本停止移动，附近的[[冷心低压|上层气旋涡流]]则在此期间逆行至系统北侧<ref name="Otto" /><ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025005753/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010051150/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010051150 | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | year = 2010 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | author = Stacy Stewart | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010051150/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010051150 }}</ref>。到10月5日时，低压槽已向北飘流至[[维尔京群岛|维尔京群岛]]上空，外界大气环境更为有利，系统内的最低气压得以向海平面延伸。低气压的结构得到改善，与邻近的上层旋涡相互作用，在加勒比海东北部上空产生广阔的[[对流|对流]][[雨带|带]]，其中包含强烈的降水和[[雷暴|雷暴]]<ref name="develop">{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-11-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121108143103/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010051749/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010051749 | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | year = 2010 | author = Stacy Stewart | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010051749/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010051749 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-18 }}</ref>。接下来几天里，系统继续发展出显著的[[亚热带气旋|亚热带天气系统结构]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook |year=2010 |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2015-10-18 |author=Robbie Berg |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120805125939/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010052357/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010052357 |archivedate=2012-08-05 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010052357/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010052357 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | year = 2010 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010060533/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010060533 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | author = Robbie Berg | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025052044/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010060533/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010060533 }}</ref>，其[[最大风速半径|风速半径]]比典型的热带气旋要大得多。卫星观测结果表明，虽然气旋内有明显的下层环流，但这些环流同西南高空的气旋状旋涡交织在一起，进一步证明系统存在多种天气系统的混合特征<ref name="ridge">{{cite web | author = Eric Blake | title = Subtropical Depression Seventeen Discussion 1 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.001.shtml? | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144525/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月6日早上6点，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]将位于[[波多黎各|波多黎各]][[圣胡安_(波多黎各)|圣胡安]]西北偏北方向约425公里的系统归类为[[亚热带气旋|亚热带低气压]]<ref name="report">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL172010_Otto.pdf | title = Hurricane Otto Tropical Cyclone Report | year = 2010 | author = John Cangialosi | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002011146/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL172010_Otto.pdf | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | date =  }}</ref>。

低气压在中大西洋上空连绵不断的上层旋涡和大规模[[高压脊|高气压区]]之间缓慢向西北方向飘移。由于前方的风切变较少，同时上层气旋预计也会逐渐减弱，因此美国国家飓风中心认为亚热带低气压有可能转变成热带气旋<ref name="ridge" />。接下来的[[卫星地图|卫星观测]]数据显示，低气压的结构急剧改善，对流带已经完全把广阔的内层风场团团包裹起来，产生时速110公里的阵风<ref>{{cite web | author = Stacy Stewart | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193456/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.003.shtml? | title = Subtropical Storm Otto Discussion 3 | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | publisher = National Hurricane Center }}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心据此于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}10月6日晚21点将位于[[大特克岛|大特克岛]]东北方向约345公里洋面的低气压升级成亚热带风暴奥托<ref>{{cite web | author = Stacy Stewart | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144521/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.public.003.shtml | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.public.003.shtml? | title = Subtropical Storm Otto Advisory 3 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。虽然卫星图像显示奥托的结构仍属典型的亚热带气旋，其中心同高空旋涡已基本并列，但[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机获得的数据表明中层环流内有暖对流核心正在发展——通常来说，这种情况都是在热带气旋的上层环流中出现<ref>{{cite web | author = Robbie Berg | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193433/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.004.shtml? | title = Subtropical Storm Otto Discussion 4 | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2014-01-02 }}</ref>。此外，气旋的大规模风场也在收缩，这证明奥托已经进入向热带气旋转变的最后阶段。虽然对流活动在夜间短暂减弱，但由于风切变不断减少，[[海面温度|海面温度]]也有显著提高，风暴于10月7日早上重新产生小股雷暴<ref>{{cite web | author = Eric Blake | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.005.shtml? | title = Subtropical Storm Otto Discussion 5 | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144542/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.005.shtml | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。气旋蜿蜒北上，多个[[数值天气预报|预测模型]]估算的温差数据表明环流内的暖心已经上升到气旋上层。随后，云层最顶端有深层热带对流爆发，中心上空温度低至零下80{{lang|en|[[摄氏度|°C]]}}<ref>{{cite web | author = Stacy Stewart | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.006.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Otto Discussion 6 | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144543/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.006.shtml }}</ref>。这样，奥托失去最后的亚热带气旋特征，成为暖芯系统，美国国家飓风中心在操作上于{{lang|en|UTC}}当天中午12点将其归类为热带气旋<ref name="report" />。

[[File:Hurricane_Otto_2010-10-09_1410Z.jpg|right]]上空逐渐减弱]]

10月8日，由于[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]近海垂直深层低压槽的影响越来越大，奥托开始加速向东北方向前进<ref name="report" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.007.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Otto Discussion 7 | year = 2010 | author = Stacy Stewart | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144544/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.007.shtml | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。高空大气环境仍然有利于气旋发展，风暴中心上空的对流深化并保持对称，形成庞大且层次分明的[[中心密集云区|中心密集云区]]<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193326/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.009.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.009.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Otto Discussion 9 | year = 2010 | author = Eric Blake | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="discussion10">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.010.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144602/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.010.shtml | title = Hurricane Otto Discussion 10 | year = 2010 | author = Todd Kimberlain | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。到{{lang|en|UTC}}中午12点，奥托的风速已达每小时120公里，还有中层[[风眼|风眼墙]]开始成形，促使美国国家飓风中心将位于[[百慕大|百慕大]]以南的气旋升级成[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|一级飓风]]<ref name="discussion10" />。风暴继续朝中大西洋的温暖海域上空前进，并因此得以进一步强化，[[特别传感微波/成像仪|微波图像]]显示有风眼形成，虽然还很模糊，但其垂直结构已经层次分明，估计奥托这时达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时140公里的最高强度<ref name="discussion12">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.012.shtml? | title = Hurricane Otto Discussion 12 | year = 2010 | author = Stacy Stewart | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144604/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.012.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | accessdate = 2010-10-08 }}</ref>。

达到最高强度时，飓风已完全嵌入到西南方向的深层气流中<ref name="discussion12" />。气旋向东北方向移动，行经洋面水温逐渐降低，上层大气环境也趋于不利，云层格局因此受到侵蚀，对流也被扰乱<ref name="discussion14">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.014.shtml? | title = Hurricane Otto Discussion 14 | year = 2010 | author = Todd Kimberlain | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144622/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.014.shtml | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Hurricane Otto Discussion 15 | year = 2010 | author = Todd Kimberlain | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144631/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.015.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.015.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref>。10月9日晚，奥托的最大持续风力时速降至110公里以下，因此降级成热带风暴<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2015-10-18 |year=2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819085839/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/text/refresh/MIATCDAT2%2Bshtml/100235.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/text/refresh/MIATCDAT2+shtml/100235.shtml |title=Tropical Storm Otto Discussion 16 |author=Stacy Stewart |publisher=National Hurricane Center |archivedate=2014-08-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。受持续不断风切变的影响，再加上缺乏热带水分补充，系统中的对流活动几近中止，气象机构因此估计风暴已开始转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.017.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144648/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.017.shtml | title = Tropical Storm Otto Discussion 17 | year = 2010 | author = Robbie Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。次日，干冷空气开始侵入微弱的暖芯，奥托也开始发展出[[锋_(气象)|锋面带状特征]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.018.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Otto Discussion 18 | year = 2010 | author = Michael Brennan | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144649/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.discus.018.shtml | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-18 }}</ref>。10月10日，风暴转变成温带气旋，美国国家飓风中心随即中止发布公告<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.public.018.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Otto Advisory 18 | year = 2010 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002144647/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al17/al172010.public.018.shtml | author = Michael Brennan | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。之后的一个星期里，奥托的温带残留在[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]附近失速，然后退化成残留低气压并向东南方向大幅回转，最终于10月18日在[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]以西洋面完全消散<ref name="report" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Otto_2010-10-07_1745z.jpg|thumb]]
奥托及其前身天气系统在加勒比地区东北部飘移了数天，给[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]北部、[[维尔京群岛|维尔京群岛]]和波多黎各大部分地区带去旷日持久的降水和阵风。局部洪灾和恶劣的海况导致大范围道路严重受损，基础设施故障，海岸沿线还有一定程度的[[海滩侵蚀|海滩侵蚀]]。风暴经过期间，许多居民家中断水停电，加勒比地区多个国家宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]。维尔京群岛和[[圣克里斯多福与尼维斯|圣克里斯多福与尼维斯]]的许多学校、商店和部分政府办事处关闭至天气状况好转时止。<ref name="lashes">{{cite news |agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]] |accessdate=2015-10-18 |author=Staff Writer |date=2010-10-08 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.smh.com.au//breaking-news-world/tropical-storm-otto-lashes-caribbean-20101008-16a50.html |title=Tropical Storm Otto lashes Caribbean |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151018154654/http://www.smh.com.au//breaking-news-world/tropical-storm-otto-lashes-caribbean-20101008-16a50.html |archivedate=2015-10-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | year = 2010 | publisher = South Florida Caribbean News | title = Tropical Storm Otto shuts down St. Kitts and Nevis | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102191933/http://sflcn.com/story.php?id=9238 | url = http://sflcn.com/story.php?id=9238 | accessdate = 2014-01-21 | author = Staff Writer | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>奥托最终在这些地区造成可观的经济损失，经初步估计数额超过2200万美元（2010年[[美元|美元]]）。此外，风暴产生的雨量还打破多项纪录，成为加勒比东北部地区历史上最潮湿的气旋之一。<ref name="wet">{{cite news | year = 2010 | publisher = The BVI Beacon | author = Webmaster | title = Drenched again}}</ref><ref name="records">{{cite web | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/sju/?n=record101001 | title = Record Rainfall 2010 San Juan | accessdate = 2015-10-18 | year = 2010 | author = SJU Webmaster | publisher = National Weather Service | archivedate = 2014-12-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141220000431/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/sju/?n=record101001 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

=== 背风群岛 ===
10月5至6日，[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]最东部沿海地区因长时间的瓢泼大雨引发持续性洪灾<ref>{{cite web |deadurl=yes |year=2010 |url=http://stluciastar.com/mp-%E2%80%98we-will-build-a-stronger-better-dennery%E2%80%99/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103212446/http://stluciastar.com/mp-%E2%80%98we-will-build-a-stronger-better-dennery%E2%80%99/ |title=We will build a stronger, better Dennery |accessdate=2014-01-03 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |author=Toni Nicholas |publisher=St. Lucia STAR }}</ref>。[[登内里区|登内里区]]有500户居民受到[[山洪爆发|山洪爆发]]的影响，这其中有400户的房屋被淹或严重受损。许多居民被迫撤离，还有一些人被困在家里<ref>{{cite web |url=http://stluciastar.com/content/archives/15981 |year=2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6MMAU0atw?url=http://stluciastar.com/dennery-disaster/ |title=Dennery Disaster |accessdate=2014-01-03 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |author=Kayra Williams |publisher=St. Lucia STAR }}</ref>。当地居民还受到缺乏饮用水和停电的困扰，并因厨房用品及其它器具丢失而无法准备膳食<ref name="dennery">{{cite web | url = http://www.caribbean360.com/news/red-cross-responds-to-st-lucia-floods | title = Red Cross responds to St Lucia floods | accessdate = 2014-01-03 | year = 2010 | publisher = Caribbean 360 | author = Staff Writer | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103233129/http://www.caribbean360.com/index.php/news/45129.html | archivedate = 2014-01-03 }}</ref>。圣卢西亚经宣告成为灾区<ref name="lashes" />，政府拨款50万[[东加勒比元|东加勒比元]]（合18万5185美元）为洪水灾民提供援助，[[红十字会与红新月会国际联合会|红十字会与红新月会国际联合会]]也从救灾应急资金拨出4万4194美元<ref name="dennery" />。

圣克里斯多福与尼维斯间接性的洪流持续了至少4天，这段时间的总计降雨量达到279毫米。许多屋主报告家中水淹情况严重，还有多人被困在家里，需要外界救援。沿海地区因阵风导致海况恶劣，导致一定程度的海滩[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]，还有一截路面边缘坍塌。降水及其引发的洪流淹没了许多桥涵和桥梁，部分道路两侧被冲毁，还有一些公用设施管线受损，对供电设施造成严重破坏。<ref>{{cite web | author = Cherisse M. Sutton-Jeffer | year = 2010 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120306025220/http://www.sknvibes.com/News/NewsDetails.cfm/15329 | deadurl = no | publisher = SKNVibes | accessdate = 2015-10-19 | url = http://www.sknvibes.com/News/NewsDetails.cfm/15329 | title = Heavy rains, high winds in SKN disrupts residents' daily routine | archivedate = 2012-03-06 }}</ref>。不过，当地的确切损失数额仍然缺乏统计。

[[File:Otto_10-06-2010_0600z.png|thumb]]以北的第十七号亚热带低气压，其大规模[[雨带|雨带]]一直延伸到加勒比地区东北部。]]

奥托在[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]产生暴雨，打破当地10月的多项降雨量纪录，[[圣托马斯岛_(美属维尔京群岛)|圣托马斯岛]]东部的红钩镇（{{lang|en|Red Hook}}）降雨量达到最高的547毫米<ref name="records" />。雨水淹没多条道路，促使官员于10月6日在全部3个岛上开设避难所<ref name="USVirgin" />。[[圣克洛伊岛|圣克洛伊岛]]通往恩菲尔德格林的道路有部分路段坍塌，附近地区的交通暂时中断至次日修出临时公路时止。该岛北岸的拉维里（{{lang|en|La Vallée}}）出现洪灾和山体滑坡，对低洼地区构成影响。<ref name="USVirgin">{{cite web |author=Joy Blackburn |year=2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313122244/http://virginislandsdailynews.com/news/storm-pummels-st-croix-1.1045082 |url=http://virginislandsdailynews.com/news/storm-pummels-st-croix-1.1045082 |publisher=Daily News Staff |archivedate=2012-03-13 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-10-19 |title=Storm pummels St. Croix }}</ref>圣托马斯岛和[[圣约翰岛_(美属处女群岛)|圣约翰岛]]的交通起初未受影响，但随着降水又持续了数天，洪水、岩崩及[[沥青混凝土|沥青]]侵蚀迫使有关部门将多条道路和高速公路封闭<ref>{{cite web |author=Joy Blackburn |author2=Aldeth Lewin |year=2010 |publisher=Daily News Staff |accessdate=2015-10-19 |archivedate=2012-03-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313122251/http://virginislandsdailynews.com/news/otto-s-onslaught-spreads-havoc-1.1045699 |url=http://virginislandsdailynews.com/news/otto-s-onslaught-spreads-havoc-1.1045699 |title=Otto's onslaught spreads havoc |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。估计这场风暴一共对美属维尔京群岛造成了200万美元损失<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313122328/http://virginislandsdailynews.com/obama-declares-hurricane-otto-was-a-disaster-for-v-i-1.1060449 |author=Constance Cooper |publisher=Virgin Island Daily News |date=2010-11-06 |accessdate=2015-10-19 |title=Obama declares Hurricane Otto was a disaster for V.I. |archivedate=2012-03-13 |deadurl=yes |url=http://virginislandsdailynews.com/obama-declares-hurricane-otto-was-a-disaster-for-v-i-1.1060449 }}</ref>。

面对气旋的威胁，[[英属维尔京群岛|英属维尔京群岛]]于10月6至8日进入山洪爆发警告生效状态<ref>{{cite news | year = 2010 | title = A Flash Flood Watch remains in effect until 6 PM today | author = Staff Writer | agency = Virgin Islands News Online}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | year = 2010 | publisher = Department of Disaster Management | accessdate = 2014-01-02 | url = http://www2.bviplatinum.com/news.php?module=news&page=Article&articleID=1286499146 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102192907/http://www2.bviplatinum.com/news.php?module=news&page=Article&articleID=1286499146 | title = Flash Flood Warning Discontinued | author = Staff Writer | archivedate = 2014-01-02 }}</ref>。各地爆发的山洪掀翻了多辆汽车，洪水还对大范围地区的公用设施管线和排水管道造成严重破坏，[[托尔托拉岛|托尔托拉岛]]（特别是[[罗德城|罗德城]]）有数十人家中断水停电<ref>{{cite news | author = CNN Wire Staff | publisher = CNN | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141209123215/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/americas/10/09/otto.virgin.islands/ | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-10-19 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/americas/10/09/otto.virgin.islands/ | title = Virgin Islands dry out after Otto's wrath | date = 2010-10-10 | archivedate = 2014-12-09 }}</ref>。当地总计降雨量高达634毫米，政府部门宣布整个群岛进入紧急状态<ref>{{cite web | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2010-10-19 | publisher = Government of the United Kingdom | title = British Virgin Islands: Governor McClary revokes state of emergency | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130918112210/http://reliefweb.int/report/british-virgin-islands/british-virgin-islands-governor-mccleary-revokes-state-emergency | author = Staff Writer | archivedate = 2013-09-18 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/british-virgin-islands/british-virgin-islands-governor-mccleary-revokes-state-emergency }}</ref>。有报道认为奥托引发了英属维尔京群岛历史上最严重的洪灾<ref name="wet" /><ref>{{cite web |publisher=Associated Press & weather.com |year=2010 |accessdate=2010-10-07 |title=Otto Floods Virgin Islands and Puerto Rico |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141119074359/http://www.weather.com/outlook/weather-news/news/articles/flooding-caribbean-otto_2010-10-07 |url=http://www.weather.com/outlook/weather-news/news/articles/flooding-caribbean-otto_2010-10-07 |author=Staff Writer |archivedate=2014-11-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，估计当地一共遭受了1050万美元损失，比一个多月前大型飓风[[2010年飓风厄尔|厄尔]]在群岛造成的损失数额要高得多<ref>{{cite web | publisher = GIS | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2010-10-21 | archivedate = 2014-01-04 | title = Statement by Premier O'Neal - Tropical Storm Otto | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104011440/http://www.bviplatinum.com/news.php?module=news&page=Article&articleID=1287690201 | url = http://www.bviplatinum.com/news.php?module=news&page=Article&articleID=1287690201 | deadurl = yes | author = Staff Writer }}</ref>。

飓风厄尔已令[[荷属圣马丁|荷属圣马丁]]的道路网络受到损伤，奥托又令破坏程度大幅上升，损失数额约为150万[[荷属安的列斯盾|荷属安的列斯盾]]（合83万8000美元）<ref>{{cite web | title = Road network damage put at over NAf 1.5 M | year = 2010 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120302052612/http://www.thedailyherald.com/islands/1-islands-news/9405-road-network-damage-put-at-over-naf-15m.html | accessdate = 2010-10-19 | publisher = The Daily Herald | author = Staff Writer | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.thedailyherald.com/islands/1-islands-news/9405-road-network-damage-put-at-over-naf-15m.html | archivedate = 2012-03-02 }}</ref>。[[圣马丁岛_(加勒比海)|圣马丁岛]]另一侧的[[法属圣马丁|法属圣马丁]]也受到洪灾影响，对基础设施产生破坏，但程度相对较轻，价值较为80万[[欧元|欧元]]（合112万美元）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://actu.orangecaraibe.com/article.php?p=44954 |title=Les dégats d'Otto |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20110811032821/http://actu.orangecaraibe.com/article.php?p=44954 |year=2010 |accessdate=2011-08-11 |publisher=Orange Caraibe |archivedate=2011-08-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 波多黎各 ===
[[File:Otto_2010_rainfall.gif|thumb]]
10月5日，波多黎各多地开始降下暴雨，部分地区甚至持续了5天之久。10月3至8日间降雨量最大的是[[葡萄牙河|葡萄牙河]]位于[[庞塞|庞塞]]境内河段，测得的雨量达454毫米<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-10-19 | year = 2010 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150410103330/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/otto2010filledrainblk.gif | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/otto2010filledrainblk.gif | title = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Puerto Rico Rainfall Map | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | format = GIF | archivedate = 2015-04-10 }}</ref>。降雨迫使[[波多黎各政府|波多黎各政府]]封闭了40多条道路，另外还有19条街道部分封锁<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.elnuevodia.com/cerradas40carreterasporlaslluvias-794002.html | title = Cerradas cuarenta carreteras por las lluvias | publisher = El Nuevo Dia | author = Frances Rosario | year = 2010 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104165014/http://www.elnuevodia.com/cerradas40carreterasporlaslluvias-794002.html | accessdate = 2010-10-07 | archivedate = 2014-01-04 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。随后爆发的大范围洪灾对至少295条道路造成影响，其中14条严重受损。据初步估计，波多黎各的道路基础设施一共遭受了价值650万美元的破坏<ref>{{cite news | title = 6.5 millones en daños en carreteras | accessdate = 2010-10-12 | author = Staff Writer | year = 2010 | publisher = Cyber News | archivedate = 2010-10-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101012184335/http://www.vocero.com/noticias/44-ultimas-noticias/15365-65-millones-en-danos-en-carreteras-por-otto.html | url = http://www.vocero.com/noticias/44-ultimas-noticias/15365-65-millones-en-danos-en-carreteras-por-otto.html }}</ref>。此外，庞塞市政府还宣布该市遭受了严重的农业损失，估计价值为150万美元<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2015-10-19 |url=http://www.periodicolaperla.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1831:cuantiosas-perdidas-en-siembras-de-cafe-citricos-y-heno&catid=81:locales&Itemid=198 |author=Reinaldo Milán |publisher=La Perla del Sur |year=2010 |title=Por el coletazo de Otto: Cuantiosas pérdidas en agricultura |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102192402/http://www.periodicolaperla.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1831%3Acuantiosas-perdidas-en-siembras-de-cafe-citricos-y-heno&catid=81%3Alocales&Itemid=198 }}</ref>。

10月7日，[[阿雷西博河|阿雷西博河]]（{{lang|es|Río Grande de Arecibo}}）开始泛滥，洪水对[[乌图阿多|乌图阿多]]一个社区的主要道路构成严重破坏，导致该社区同周边的交通中断。此后不久，一条电线杆因山体滑坡倒在路上，导致大型车辆（包括救护生）无法通行。山体滑坡还令庞塞14户人家被困，一套位于路边的住房严重受损，住户被迫疏散。[[卡耶伊|卡耶伊]]有一个社区因桥梁坍塌而同周边地区失去联系。当地还因河流泛滥引发街道洪灾，数十户居民被困在家中。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.elnuevodia.com/familiasincomunicadasenareciboponceycayey-794233.html | publisher = El Nuevo Dia | author = Joel Ortiz Rivera | year = 2010 | title = Familias incommunicadas en Arecibo, Ponce y Cayey | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104211249/http://www.elnuevodia.com/familiasincomunicadasenareciboponceycayey-794233.html | accessdate = 2014-01-04 | archivedate = 2014-01-04 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>严重的洪灾还污染了水源，导致约4万5000人在风暴过后缺乏饮用水。政府为此宣布全岛进入紧急状态，有关部门一共开设了120个避难所，另外还有许多洪水灾民需要救援。<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-09-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120915015702/http://www.elnuevodia.com/estadodeemergenciaentodalaisla-794673.html | url = http://www.elnuevodia.com/estadodeemergenciaentodalaisla-794673.html | title = Más carreteras cerradas, 45,000 sin agua y sobre 120 refugiados | publisher = El Nuevo Dia | author = Joel Ortiz Rivera | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2012-10-08 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>

